,"tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-hearts-al-qulub","tag-manners-adab","tag-parables-amthal","tag-purification-of-the-soul-tazkiyyat-al-nafs"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-av8","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17563,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/11\/best-thing-khuluq-hasan-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":40370,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Good character best thing given by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 11, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: I witnessed bedouins ask the Prophet, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the best thing a servant may be given?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGood character.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3436 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33065,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/03\/know-your-best-deed-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":40370,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Know your best deed is the prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRemain upright, though you cannot encompass it entirely. Know that the most favorable of your deeds is prayer and that none can preserve his ablution but a believer.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 278 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10000,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/25\/qadr-increase-life-span-repel\/","url_meta":{"origin":40370,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Righteousness increases life span, repels evil fate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe span of life is not increased but by righteousness, and the divine decree is not repelled but by supplication. Verily, a man is deprived of provision due to\u00a0the sins he commits.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 90\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/11\/02\/treat-women-best-way\/","url_meta":{"origin":40370,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Women: Best men treat women in best manner","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of you are the best to their women.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1978 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u06